<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <% if(endpoint == 'signin') { %>
        <title>Sign in</title>
    <% } else if(endpoint == 'signup') { %>
        <title>Sign up</title>
    <% } else { %>
        <title>University</title>
    <% } %>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
                <div class="container">
                    <a href="/"><img src="logo.png" alt="logo"></a>
                <ul>
                    <% if(endpoint == 'signin') { %>
                        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/signup">Sign up</a></li>
                    <% } else if(endpoint == 'signup') { %>
                        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/signin">Sign in</a></li>
                    <% } else if(endpoint == 'home' && auth == true){ %>
                        <li>
                            <form method="post" action="/signout" >
                                <input type="submit" value="Sign out"/>
                            </form>
                        </li>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <li><a href="/signin">Signin</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/signup">Signup</a></li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">About us</a></li>
                <li><a href="/books">Books</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact us</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="content">
                <% if(endpoint == 'signin') { %>
                    <h2>Sign in</h2><br>
                    <form method="post" action="/signin">
                        <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="Username" required><br>
                        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required><br><br>
                        <div id="error-message"><%= error %></div>
                        <input type="submit" id="submit" value="Sign in">
                    </form>
                <% } else if(endpoint == 'signup') { %>
                    <h2>Sign up</h2><br>
                    <form method="post" action="/signup">
                        <input type="text" id="username" name="username" placeholder="Username" required><br>
                        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required><br><br>
                        <div id="error-message"><%= error %></div>
                        <input type="submit" id="submit" value="Sign up">
                    </form> 
                <% } else { %>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed accumsan, ex nec condimentum fermentum, purus ex venenatis erat, ac vulputate dui libero sit amet nulla. Quisque sit amet tincidunt ipsum, eu bibendum eros. Donec ac urna quis nisi rhoncus malesuada. Fusce vitae vulputate dolor. Integer auctor massa eget libero consequat, vitae volutpat nunc efficitur. Etiam nec enim vitae ante volutpat fermentum non non ligula. Praesent aliquet orci a augue hendrerit, id dictum elit pharetra. Nam laoreet ultrices quam, eu mattis ligula varius in.</p>
                <% } %>            
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>
    <footer>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/"  target="_blank"><img src="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/instagram-glyph-1.svg" alt="Instegram"></a></li>
            <li><a href="https://twitter.com/?lang=en" target="_blank"><img src="https://about.twitter.com/content/dam/about-twitter/x/brand-toolkit/logo-black.png.twimg.1920.png" alt="X"></a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com" target="_blank"><img src="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/linkedin-icon-1.svg" alt="linkedin"></a></li>
            <li><a href="/https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank"><img src="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/facebook-icon-1.svg" alt="facebook"></a></li>
        </ul>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>